---
title: Chicken Sausage Gemelli with Parmesan
description: A bowl of pasta never fails to satisfy—it’s quick, carby, comforting, and our total weeknight go-to. When you add Italian chicken sausage, sweet peas, and Parmesan to the equation, you’ve reached another level of deliciousness entirely. Ready to enjoy bite after bite of twisty gemelli pasta cloaked in this creamy, flavorful, lemon-spiked sauce? We thought so.
